html.htmlText: Beverly Hills Architectural Designer Luxury Home surrounded by incredible Celebrity houses.  Spa-like resort, private sun filled suite, and jacuzzi.  A fabulous 5 Star Super Host home with private outside dining, private entrance,  fine Italian sheets, housekeeping services and custom designer bathroom.  A quiet oasis close to downtown Rodeo drive.    A luxury suite with all the amenities.  Relax in peaceful decadence, perfect for solo guests and couples.

Private suite in multi-million dollar luxury designer home in the "Estate Section" of Beverly Hills, surrounded by lush vegetation, shade trees, private entrance, private bath, poolside entrance to the room, big screen TV, cable and blazing fast Wi-Fi (Spectrum). Great location for work and vacation sight-seeing anywhere in Los Angeles area. Hiking trails adjacent.

Bedroom has top quality mattress, down pillows, private patio, private entrance, and private security. It has pressed sheets and a 48 inch flat screen TV.

Additional perks: housekeeping services twice a week

Private bedroom, bathroom, access to a mind-blowing large kitchen and all it has to offer.   If guests use the 2nd guest bathroom that is available to them at additional cost. 24 hour notice for pool heating and surcharges will be applied.
Co-host will help with any needs you have, information for getting around town, restaurants to go to, clubs to check out, cool places to see and fun stuff to do!

You will have a private entrance, parking spot, security code, shared kitchen.

features.title: Booking Protection Guarantee
features.subtitle: In the unlikely event a Host needs to cancel your booking within 30 days of check-in, we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Check-In Guarantee
features.subtitle: If you can’t check into your home and the Host cannot resolve the issue, we’ll find you a similar or better home for the length of your original stay, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Get-What-You-Booked Guarantee
features.subtitle: If at any time during your stay you find your listing isn't as advertised—for example, the refrigerator stops working and your Host can’t easily fix it, or it has fewer bedrooms than listed—you'll have three days to report it and we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

content.htmlText: Extremely high-end neighborhood filled with celebrities and famous people who live in Beverly Hills.  There is no other place like this, and a terrific opportunity to say "you were here" or just enjoy the finer things in life. Peaceful, quiet and beautiful, very relaxing. You may not want to leave. Vista filled hiking trails within walking distance. The house is 5 minutes from Beverly Glen Circle's Starbucks, restaurants, shopping, dry cleaning, etc.

Extremely high-end neighborhood filled with celebrities and famous people who live in Beverly Hills.  There is no other place like this, and a terrific opportunity to say "you were here" or just enjoy the finer things in life. Peaceful, quiet and beautiful, very relaxing. You may not want to leave. Vista filled hiking trails within walking distance. The house is 5 minutes from Beverly Glen Circle's Starbucks, restaurants, shopping, dry cleaning, etc.

This is in the secluded hills above Los Angeles. Best to either have a car, or you can find a plethora of Uber/Lyft drivers that will pick you up and drive you around town. Mass transit at the base of the hills, either on Beverly Hills side or Sherman Oaks side.

section.about:
I am a professional Interior Designer who has had her own business for 35 years.  I have made a living out of making a house beautiful and providing luxury LifeStyles to the rich and famous.  
  I love to dine out but  I live in a quiet environment with no drama.  My home is immaculate, sunny and safe in a high residential area.  
I am a SUPER HOST and love helping my guest find interesting things to do and restaurants to visit that they may not have known of.  I have truly enjoyed hosting some of the most fabulous people.  You will not be disappointed!  Hiking, Jazz clubs and great places to eat are very near.

hostHighlights.title: Where I went to school: West Virginia Mountain Mama
Fun fact: I have been in Architectural Digest
What makes my home unique: Beauty, Serenity, location

Beverly Hills Architectural Designer Luxury Home surrounded by incredible Celebrity houses. Spa-like resort, private sun filled suite, and jacuzzi. A fabulous 5 Star Super Host home with private outside dining, private entrance, fine Italian sheets, housekeeping services and custom designer bathroom. A quiet oasis close to downtown Rodeo drive. A luxury suite with all the amenities. Relax in peaceful decadence, perfect for solo guests and couples.

The space
Private suite in multi-million dollar luxury designer home in the "Estate Section" of Beverly Hills, surrounded by lush vegetation, shade trees, private entrance, private bath, poolside entrance to the room, big screen TV, cable and blazing fast Wi-Fi (Spectrum). Great location for work and vacation sight-seeing anywhere in Los Angeles area. Hiking trails adjacent.

Bedroom has top quality mattress, down pillows, private patio, private entrance, and private security. It has pressed sheets and a 48 inch flat screen TV.

Additional perks: housekeeping services twice a week

Guest access
Private bedroom, bathroom, access to a mind-blowing large kitchen and all it has to offer. If guests use the 2nd guest bathroom that is available to them at additional cost. 24 hour notice for pool heating and surcharges will be applied.

During your stay
Co-host will help with any needs you have, information for getting around town, restaurants to go to, clubs to check out, cool places to see and fun stuff to do!

Other things to note
You will have a private entrance, parking spot, security code, shared kitchen.
